EN: Beliefs are an important part of people's lives.
ZH: 学会尊重他人的信仰是很重要的。
EN: Learning to respect others' beliefs is important.
ZH: 信仰可以给人带来内心的平静。
EN: Beliefs can bring inner peace to people.
