EN: Everyone has the right to choose their beliefs.
ZH: 信仰能够引导我们做出正确的选择。
EN: Beliefs can guide us to make the right choices.
ZH: 我们应该尊重不同人的信仰。
EN: We should respect different people's beliefs.
